This is the README file for the afterParty project. 

The main afterParty documentation is maintained here:

https://github.com/mojones/AfterParty2/wiki

This repository contains the whole directory structure for a Grails project. A brief description of the structure of the repository is as follow:

grails-app : contains classes for the Grails web framework
lib        : contains Java libraries required by afterParty
sample_data: contains example datasets for testing
src        : contains Java and Groovy scripts used in the development of afterParty
test       : contains unit testing for Grails code - not currently used
web-app    : contains static resources (images, stylesheets, javascript) for the web application

Please submit bug reports, features requests, etc. to martin.jones@ed.ac.uk

